I"a<p>This snippet is useful for highlighting multiple keywords in search results:</p>
<div class="language-javascript highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="kd">var</span> <span class="nx">searchResult</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="dl">"</span><span class="s2">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consetetur sadipscing elitr</span><span class="dl">"</span>
